WEBVTT

00:02:59.442 --> 00:03:02.501
and reimagine an entire world
designed for touch.

00:03:03.620 --> 00:03:06.343
And on November 5, 2017,

00:03:07.446 --> 00:03:10.358
Wayband helped a person who was blind

00:03:10.382 --> 00:03:13.164
run the first 15 miles
of the New York City Marathon

00:03:13.188 --> 00:03:15.141
without any sighted assistance.

00:03:15.165 --> 00:03:21.745
(Applause)

00:03:23.744 --> 00:03:26.761
It didn't get him through the entire race
due to the heavy rain,

00:03:26.785 --> 00:03:27.975
but that didn't matter.

00:03:27.999 --> 00:03:29.006
(Laughter)

00:03:29.030 --> 00:03:30.244
We had proved the point: